After 🦠 clean with me 

Alexander just got over the stomach 🦠 . So today I spent the day deep cleaning all the surfaces & linens in my home the  areas he was laying down on , trying my best to sanitize my home. 

I’ll be lying if I didn’t tell you I wasnt scared yesterday when he was sick 🤕

I think I might have over reacted because I started googling & reading the news my anxiety was at a all time high . 
Thank god he just had the stomach bug & is feeling 100 better today 💕

here is how I cleaned my home 🏠 

first opened up all the windows letting my home air out 
Next I washed Alexander’s bedding , I washed all the throw pillows and blankets he was laying on . I also wiped all the surfaces with bleach & water 💦 wiped down the stair way , the walls , door knobs & light switches . I also cleaned all the bathrooms & kitchen . I didn’t share that here because I think you already know my kitchen and bathroom cleaning routine .. 

With that being said I have much plans coming up next week and so on .

My kids schooling & Alexander being sick threw me off course . Next week I should be back in action to share with you all the content I have in store 🍂

Have a wonderful weekend!

It’s a lovely day today 🍃 

Opening up all the windows 🪟 & airing out my home today . I love to grab fresh herbs & fruit and a few drops of essential oils to freshen up my home . 

I used fresh rosemary bunch , orange & and sandalwood essential oil . I use a pot and fill it with water 💧 & simmer it on my stove . It smells Devine ! If you like cashmere scent you definitely should give that a try! 

Also I hung the new mirror I bought from @hobbylobby .. not sure if I’ll keep it here 🤔 what do you suggest? Let me know 

Have a wonderful day!
